American-Statesman) (f, l)
</P>
<P>
   ONLINE-DEALS _ Online merchants want your business, and they're
going to great lengths to get it. The Web is rife with offers of
free this and free that. Shipping, merchandise, dollars off _
merchants will give a lot to get you to shop with them. Here is a
small sampling of the deals that await. (Austin American-Statesman)
(f, l)
</P>
<P>
   ONLINE-SITES _ We've compiled a list of some interesting places
to shop online. In addition to those listed here, many name-brand
retailers and manufacturers have Web sites; they're usually pretty
easy to find. (Austin American-Statesman) (f, l)
</P>
<P>
   ONLINE-COLUMN _ Will malls, with their color-coded directories,
greasy food courts and parking lots stretching out past forever,
die out? Part of me hopes so. There's Darwinism afoot, and right
now, e-commerce sites have the edge. It's easier. You don't deal
with crowds or parking. You don't even pay tax. It's inherently
appealing, easy, safer than you'd think. (Gallaga, Austin
American-Statesman) (f, l)
</P>
