   BASKETBALL/PROS
</P>
<P>
   BKN-HAWKS _ How will the Hawks compensate for the loss of Jim
Jackson, who is expected to miss at least a week after knee
surgery? Two of the players likely to step up will be Roshown
McLeod and Chris Crawford. The loss of Jackson will hurt the team,
which has won four straight games, but the Hawks have a pair of
winnable games this week against the Los Angeles Clippers and
Golden State Warriors. (Denberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
