   POLIO-VACCINE (Undated) _ The American Academy of Pediatrics
will recommend injected dead polio vaccine for all four doses,
beginning Jan. 1. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention made
the same recommendation earlier this year. Dead virus vaccine
causes fewer cases of polio. By Karen Hsu. 600 words.
</P>
<P>
   MA-FIRE-WORCESTER -- (Worcester, Mass.) _ Anguish turns to
frustration as firefighters are forced to abandon their search for
five fallen comrades inside a burned-out warehouse after an 80-foot
firewall threatens to collapse. By Marcella Bombardieri. 900 words.
</P>
