<P>
   ZIFF-SELLOFF (Undated) _ Publishing giant Ziff-Davis will sell
off most of its holdings, including PC Week, the famed computer
magazine. By Steven Wilmsen. 650 words.
</P>
<P>
   CABLE-ATT (Undated) _ Advocates of open access to cable modems
slam ATT-Mindspring ``deal'' as a smokescreen that means nothing.
Mindspring customers wouldn't get access to ATT fast cable modems
until 2002 at the soonest. By Peter Howe. 600 words.
</P>
