r a BC-QUOTE-OF-THE-DAY-NYT     12-06 0061
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-QUOTE-OF-THE-DAY-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-SCI-MARS-LANDER-NYT, which moved
in ``a'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``Man, it's tough when you put that much work for years into
designing, building and testing; it's hard to lose it all.''
</P>
<P>
   _WAYNE F. ZIMMERMAN a Mars Polar Lander engineer.
</P>
