   TV-`MILLIONAIRE' &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Making ``Who Wants to Be a Millionaire'' a regular
series is great for ABC, but what about the rest of us? Its
popularity can't possibly be good for the short-term future of
television. By KEN PARISH PERKINS. Story will move in ``e''
entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
