Express flights there, and  &UR; Betsy Nolan &LR; , visiting there from San
Francisco, says the Sydney Morning Herald wondered whether it was
smart ``to fly with an airline that doesn't go all the way.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Comedian and director  &UR; Eric Idle &LR;  told Biography magazine that
if he were to choose one stand-up comic for a stay on a desert
island, it would be  &UR; Robin Williams &LR; . ``We always go on holiday
together,'' and said, ``and we go shopping together. If you know
Robin very well, he can actually stop having to be funny.''
</P>
<P>
   _  &UR; Firat Yener &LR;  read in Ambassador magazine that one guest at
San Francisco's Triton Hotel stole a duvet, drapes, shower curtain,
soap dishes, pillows and towels.
</P>
<P>
